To set up buttons:

mkdir ~/.Control
mkdir ~/.Control/systemd

cp ~/WebControl/MaslowButton.service ~/.Control/systemd

mkdir ~/.WebControl/systemd
cp MaslowButton.py ~/.WebControl/systemd

that is all for the button and LED service.

To set up the bluetooth wii remote as a pendant input, copy these files also

cp ~/WebControl/MaslowPendant.service ~/.Control/systemd

cp MaslowPendant.py ~/.WebControl/systemd

This service requires the installation of the cwiid library compiled for python 3